cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use MOLEKUL in your research or teaching, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "MOLEKUL: A Pure-Python Ab Initio Quantum Chemistry Code for Education and Reproducible Benchmarking"
version: "0.1.1"
date-released: "2026-04-24"
